                  </rs>. <hi rend="largeCaps">BEALE</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">was further charged with a previous conviction at the Mansion House in December</hi>, 1877, <hi rend="italic">to which he</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY></hi>.**—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18780916-802-punishment-55" type="punishmentDescription">
